title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The 2020 Throwing Fits Year in Review Critics’ Choice Awards Spectacular Christmas Eve Special
description:
Stop whatever it is you’re doing because the Core 4 are reconvening to debate, discuss and crown their personal favorite jawnz, brands, collabs, trends, sneakers, footwear, TV shows, musical artists, best-dressed celebs and bozos of the the most ass year in recent history. Plus, an opportunity for you to cast your votes as we put a bow on the turd that is 2020.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
